text:
Prepacked mala cold dishes. Not very fascinating.

Mala scallop is not bad. Member has discount. $7plus a box (original price $12).

Mala king oyster mushroom not as nice. Look like it is soaked in the mala very long and lost its mushroom crunchiness.

Mala beancurd skin tasted ok.

But for a small box like that, to sell at $6plus $7plus, is actually not cheap. Luckily there is grab dineout discount, which makes it not too expensive.

No dine in. Its just a store where you buy and go.
Great food, impeccable service Easy parking
Helpful staff. Moved out of the original shop space, but new stall is right next to it within the same mall.
Please remove @Cityvibe is confusing. This shop is in Grantral Mall
Keep on vomiting after eating duck wings
